        <li>►Improving search engine ranking and visibility</li>
        <li>►Building trust among new visitors through accurate availability and demand signals</li>
        <li>►Generating better analytics for pricing and marketing strategy</li>
        <li>►Preventing false or duplicate bookings, ensuring clean and transparent data</li>
    </ul>
